  Tui3 Eng2-hok-so2 koe3-sin sng3 khi2 tu2 10 ni5 e5 7 goeh8 poaN3, hit jit8 chin joah8, A-thiam-m2 ti7 chhu3-au7 hiahN chha5, m7-chai chaiN2-iuN7 sio koe7-kha soa3 poah8 loh8-khi3, thau5-khak siang3 tui3 chioh8-thau5 loh8-khi3, tai7-khai3 si7 nau2 chin2-tong7, a2-si7 nau2-kin tng7-khi3, in-ui7 i chin hoat-hok, peng5-si5 hiat-ap ia7 chin koan5, tiaN7 kio3 thau5-khak gong5, sou2-i2 hun7-khi3 chin ku2, kiu3 cheng-sin5 chhiaN2 i-seng lai5 khoaN3, sui-jian5 u7 chu3-sia7, chiah8 ioh8 long2 bo5 kong-hau7, lang5 bin5-bin5 bo5 siaN2 chai lang5, an2-ni u7 jit8-goa7 chiu7 lai5 li7-khui se3-kan. TaN chia m7-bian2 siong5-se3 kong2. Kong2 Eng2-hok-hiaN hit ni5 tu2 40 hoe3. TaN ka-chai3 toa7 cha-bou2-kiaN2 Lan5-eng ia7 17 hoe3 lah, tai7-khai3 ke-lai7 e5 su7 tou long2 e7-hiau2 choe3, sou2-i2 bo5 kam2-kak sim2-mih8 toa7 khun3-lan5. Te7-ji7 cha-bou2-kiaN2 Lan5-hiong 14 hoe3, tu2 pit-giap8 kok-bin5 hak8-hau7, chun2-pi7 beh kho2 chhou-tiong. Te7 saN cha-bou2-kiaN2 Lan5-ji5 11 hoe3, kok-bin5 hak8-hau7 saN lian5 thak8 liau2 beh koe3 si3-lian5. Chit8 ke ia7 si7 chin lau7-jiat8, Eng2-hok hiaN chin thiaN3 chiah-e5 kiaN2, chiah-e5 kiaN2 ia7 chin iu2-hau3. Toa7-che2 Lan5-eng teng2 in lau7-bu2 e5 khoeh, ia7 si7 chin oah8-tang7 gau5 pang-chan7 Chu2-jit8-oh8 kap gim5-si-pan. Eng2-hok-hiaN siuN7 kong2 ai3 kha-chhiu2, chiu7 ti7 keh ni5 Lan5-eng 18 hoe3 ni5-boe2, khoaN3 u7 tu2-ho2 siang7 kau3-hoe7 e5 chheng-lian5, chiu7 ka7 i chio jip8--lai5. Kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3 e5 an-pai5, chin-chiaN3 tit-tioh8 chin ho2 e5 kiaN2-sai3. I ia7 chin kong-to7, chin-chiaN3 si7 ho2 pa-pah. Chiu7-si7 chiong in tiuN7-lang5 cha2 e5 giap8, long2 teng-ki3 hou7 in toa7 cha-bou2-kiaN2, phin2 na7 seN toa7 sun, tioh8 koh thng5 chit8 e5 seN3 Bok8. Tui3 an2-ni kiaN2-sai3 ia7 chin kam2-sim in tiuN7-lang5 e5 ho2-i3, chin iu2-hau3 khiN5 ke. Chiah-e5 tai7-chi3 an3-ha7 bian2 kong2. 
